Package io.openems.edge.evcs.api

Interface MetaEvcs

All Superinterfaces:
Evcs, OpenemsComponent
All Known Subinterfaces:
EvcsClusterPeakShaving
All Known Implementing Classes:
EvcsClusterPeakShavingImpl
public interface MetaEvcs extends Evcs
A MetaEvcs is a wrapper for physical electric vehicle charging stations. It is not a physical Evcs itself. This is used to distinguish e.g. an EvcsCluster from an actual Evcs.
